# Frontend Environment Variables
#
# Local dev: leave VITE_API_URL unset (or empty) so requests use /api and Vite proxies to localhost:5000.
# Production (CI): set GitHub secret VITE_API_URL to your HTTPS API CloudFront base, e.g.:
#   https://d3cvs28uau3ofy.cloudfront.net/api
# Do NOT use http://elasticbeanstalk.com — browsers block HTTP API calls from HTTPS CloudFront (mixed content).
# See .env.production.example for the current production value.
#
# Optional — bypass proxy and call backend directly while developing:
#VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
